        public Builder​(java.lang.String accessToken)
        Create a new GetUsersTopTracksRequest.Builder instance.

        Getting details of a user's top tracks requires authorization of the user-top-read scope.

        Parameters:
        accessToken - Required. A valid access token from the Spotify Accounts service.
        See Also:
        Spotify: Using Scopes

      • time_range

        public GetUsersTopTracksRequest.Builder time_range​(java.lang.String time_range)
        The time range setter.
        Parameters:
        time_range - Optional. Over what time frame the affinities are computed. Valid values: long_term (calculated from several years of data and including all new data as it becomes available), medium_term (approximately last 6 months), short_term (approximately last 4 weeks). Default: medium_term.
        Returns:
        A GetUsersTopTracksRequest.Builder.
